data.description: Located right off of US Highway 183, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage (tandem) house with solar panels in Leander is ready for you to move in! Make your way into the living area that showcases pristine tile flooring, lots of windows, and is open to the kitchen. The kitchen features an island, granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Either choose to enjoy your meal in the dining area or outside on the covered patio in the backyard. The extended covered patio is built with almost no maintenance composite and has an amazing hot tub for relaxing evenings. Retreat into the primary bedroom that highlights an en suite bathroom including, separated dual sinks, a large shower, and a walk-in closet. Located right next to downtown Leander, enjoy the convenience of being near all your favorite restaurants, shops, and fun attractions! 2.25% existing loan can be assumed - buyer must qualify.
